<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1755444-what-is-a-gold-font-as-described-gifted">What is a &#39;gold font&#39; as described gifted by Queen Elizabeth 1 to James VI? It throwing me off a bit because all I can find are gold letters of the alphabet in google.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1755444'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F16033.Mary_Queen_of_Scotland_and_The_Isles">like</a></span>

