<div id="review_2650231008" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2650231008" />
    <a title="Quirkyreader" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5355311-quirkyreader"><img alt="Quirkyreader" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1452716553p2/5355311.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2650231008?book_show_action=true">Dec 18, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Quirkyreader" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Quirkyreader" href="/user/show/5355311-quirkyreader">Quirkyreader</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780312082628" href="/book/show/1186301.Mary_Queen_of_Scotland_and_the_Isles">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2650231008" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2362104716113635793">It took almost a year because other books got in the way. Now I am finally done.<br/><br/>This was a wonderfully written piece of historical fiction about one of the most misunderstood monarchs of Scotland.<br/><br/>When you get started on this, make sure that other books don’t get in the way. It is a chunkster that requires time to complete and savour. I’m glad I took the time to finish this one.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


